            <p><strong>Information collected:</strong> Service usage status (access status, traffic, routing, etc.)</p>
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Analysis of usage status and service improvement based on it</p>
            <p><strong>How to stop information collection:</strong> Information collection can be stopped through browser settings using Google's "Google Analytics Opt-out Add-on".</p>
          </div>
          
          <h3>2. Microsoft Clarity</h3>
          <div class="tool-info">
            <p><strong>Provider:</strong> Microsoft Corporation</p>
            <p><strong>Information collected:</strong> Heatmap data and session recordings of behavior on the Service (clicks, scrolls, dwell time, etc.)</p>
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Analysis for UI/UX improvement</p>
            <p><strong>How to stop information collection:</strong> Can be stopped using Microsoft's opt-out function. Please refer to the company's privacy statement for details.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

